Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星外实习作业中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏茜玛斯喀维校学生一名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然失去联络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能滞留在C42废弃设施中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完成后第一时间前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布斯那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己瞎走才遇难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是自作自受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧气应该已经用完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全校一霸就此完蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆的实习艇真的不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真打算去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想的 亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会被连累死的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 有人进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急救措施 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 同学 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 等在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏迷中 但还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 紧急送医
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不等救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样说不定…会来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时阿布斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧气罐残量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是零了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人可是阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记他怎么对我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着有一线生机的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能见死不救… 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}（欢庆毕业）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 装饰得好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一二年级生准备的惊喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 让我们典礼结束来活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来早了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片打算留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这张 好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可以留下它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是发你数码照了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的是贴在这里的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽是继续读书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 本来是这么打算的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…想重新考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时呆在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆要入伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假期结束以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个月以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和学校一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…要加入军队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没告诉过你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面那样子 比上军校好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么听话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能帮更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了当兵 还有很多帮助人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗可不是慈善事业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在是战争年代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参战是保护别人的最佳途径
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆要自立了 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎终于找到了 自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己力所能及的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太装模作样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业典礼要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位亲爱的毕业生们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我想请两位同学代表大家上台发言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请上台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长又心血来潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 自己一辈子都不会忘记这里的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想对朋友 想对大家说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 当我们第一天认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个机动战士痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们平时有多迁就你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威！你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你们 每天才这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宪兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以泄漏机密罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即间谍罪 拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有拒绝的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见吗 间谍嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 可能这家伙自己就是「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特不是的 他是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学 老实一点会对你有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前 你刚转学来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘就开始袭击托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常出现可疑的电波通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次攻击前后 通讯频率增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要辩解就先去基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间吻合 只因为这种理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就怀疑杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审查任何一个有嫌疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是维甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们… 在一起好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来妨碍调查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想尝尝蹲牢房的滋味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说杰哈特骗我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他才是维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放他跑 追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 受伤没？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 你从不会怀疑人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:13:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去卫生室吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意 保持队列
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地毯式排查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 逃进这么棘手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小队 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一只蚂蚁也别放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达斯 多亏你引起骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到撤的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吩咐Dorado队待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始执行占领托尔迪亚的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许停留得太久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前确认4台维甘机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台来自卫星外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台似乎潜伏在卫星内的丘陵地带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上任不久就有一展身手的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘考虑得真是周到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本队前往迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 外星佬面前我看谁敢装孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 刚才逃走的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘进攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星守军难堪重任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 你也出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经装车往你那里运了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到学校门前的大路上等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里 或许有过我渴求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有 忘记故乡的惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种虚伪的安宁 不是战士需要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘给我 滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还留在这座卫星里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶的人是 亚瑟姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全部被看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR 果然无法跟上我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对高达 不能将就啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是那种自愿走上战场的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会 在那东西上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是… 维甘吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们生在不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗了…我们吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和你的话 也许能一直做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我作为战士肩负着责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有无法让步的 为之而战的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗 这样的觉悟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是我 你能下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种善良的家伙 不适合战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种善良的家伙 不适合战斗
